    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It lasted five minutes and, then, it's the same story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was-- that was one instance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the worst thing was to-- they used to give us a shower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, naked, we had to stand in the snow in Appel, and-- and counting us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So you can imagine how many survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any cruel-- cruelty that they could think of, they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many-- yes, sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
